    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka hikes kerosene price 290-pct in steep correction",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Economynext \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s petroleum corporation has hiked the price of kerosene by 253 rupees to 340 rupees per litre with effect from midnight Sunday, August 21.",
        "Kerosene was sold at 87 rupees but was out of stock in the market as Sri Lanka\u2019s sole oil refinery that produced kerosene remained shut due to a shortage of crude oil shipments.",
        "The ministry announced on Saturday that the refinery will be run for at least 40 days as it has purchased two consignments of Russian crude oil. (Colombo/Aug21/2022)"
      ],
